messages.speech: Joint Entrance Examination (JEE) is an engineering entrance examination conducted for admission to various engineering colleges in India. It is constituted by two different examinations - JEE Main and the JEE Advanced. The exams are of the objective pattern. It is an entrance test conducted for Engineering and Architecture courses . For more information about the colleges providing the course, you can visit- https://www.toppr.com/bytes/architecture-colleges-through-jee/
